snippet.textDisplay: For all those wondering what all the German "Justin" and "Reaktionsboss" comments are about, there's a German fashion YouTuber named Justin who does a lot of of reaction videos to jewelry collections and GQ 'On the Rocks' and he (jokingly) calls himself the 'boss' of things, so when reacting to videos he is the 'Reaktionsboss' meaning the 'reaction boss'.
